reviewText: Although, 8 movies in two discs may be too abundant, more than 50% of these movies provide plenty of action and suspense.
Its not the best movie pack.  I got it for the Wahlberg movie....The Yards and Ordinary Decent Criminals.
A good collection of movies with some drama and a bit of action.
It was ok nothing more to say on this movie
NOwhere does it list WHAT movies are on it.
Bought this as a gift for a friend that loves all action films!  He liked all of them!
For $5 its a steal, though I only bought it for My Name is Modesty, there a few other jewels on here (not all of them)
